They say you can pick up your car.

05:28.246 --> 05:29.931
What's the damage?

05:30.321 --> 05:32.831
<i>- They didn't say on the machine.
- Oh, that's a great sign!</i>

05:34.183 --> 05:35.556
Hello?

05:36.674 --> 05:38.921
