have been released...</i>

06:39.818 --> 06:42.593
<i>...suspect's here.
Do they have any leads?</i>

06:43.028 --> 06:44.958
<i>- Yeah?
- Are you watching the news, chief?</i>

06:45.386 --> 06:47.513
Er, yeah, you know I gotta stay
on top of the topical shit.

06:48.017 --> 06:50.349
<i>The TV boys say the
suspect is 16.</i>

06:50.962 --> 06:54.533
<i>Ten bucks says the SFK winds
up here in your class tomorrow.</i>

06:55.145 --> 06:58.424
<i>- Why would he be Special Handling? - You
can get by with a lot of shit in this world</i>

06:58.788 --> 07:01.929
<i>but you can't stab a retarded
kid and not be Special Handling.</i>

07:02.235 --> 07:03.376
